short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_U: Autofill login forms and store web passwords in Team Password Manager
short.cs: Automatické vyplňování přihlašovacích formulářů a ukládání webových hesel v aplikaci Team Password Manager
short.de: Login-Formulare automatisch ausfüllen und Passwörter in Team Password Manager speichern
short.es: Autocompletar formularios de inicio de sesión y almacenar contraseñas web en Team Password Manager
short.fr: Remplir automatiquement les formulaires de connexion et stocker les mots de passe Web dans Team Password Manager
short.pt_BR,pt_PT: Completa formulários de login automaticamente e armazena senhas da web no Team Password Manager

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Team Password Manager Chrome Extension allows Chrome users to fill in login forms from credentials stored in Team Password Manager. This extension also allows to store web passwords in Team Password Manager.

Team Password Manager is a self hosted web based password manager for groups.
